OL,3,C'Porch pirates' on the rise: What
OL,4,Cshould you do if your parcel is stolen?
OL,6,FThe average value of stolen goods
OL,7,Fincreased by 52% - rising from #66.50
OL,8,Fin 2023 to #102 this year.
OL,10,FHowever, only one in 333 thefts are
OL,11,Freported to the police.
OL,13,FSo what should you do if you think
OL,14,Fyour parcel is stolen?
OL,16,FContact the seller
OL,18,FUnder consumer law, the seller is
OL,19,Fresponsible for making sure parcels
OL,20,Fare delivered.
