OL,3,C'Porch pirates' on the rise: What
OL,4,Cshould you do if your parcel is stolen?
OL,6,FIf you think your parcel has been
OL,7,Fstolen, you should contact the person
OL,8,For company that sent the item.
OL,10,FThe retailer should offer you a refund
OL,11,For replacement if the parcel is
OL,12,Fstolen, missing or damaged.
OL,14,FIf a courier was used to deliver the
OL,15,Fitem, the seller should contact them
OL,16,Fto find out what's happened to the
OL,17,Fparcel, Citizens Advice said.
OL,19,FWhat about if the parcel was stolen
OL,20,Ffrom a safe place?
